- 🗄️ Database tasks:    [N]
- 🏛️ Domain tasks:      [N]
- 📦 Application tasks: [N]
- 🔧 Infrastructure:    [N]
- 🌐 API/UI tasks:      [N]
- 🧪 Testing tasks:     [N]
- 📝 Doc tasks:         [N]
- ⚠️ Blocked tasks:     [N]
──────────────────────────
   Total: [N] tasks

🚀 Bước tiếp theo:
  Để bắt đầu implement, gõ:
  /implement docs/tasks/tasks_[feature-name].md
  
  Hoặc chỉ định task cụ thể:
  /implement docs/tasks/tasks_[feature-name].md --task DB-01
```

